text:
Comments 
Alabama beat reporters John Talty and Matt Zenitz discuss the good and bad factors from from Saturday's Texas A&M game in the Monday beat reporter show. Watch the video above to see what they focus on, and see the game gallery below. 
Alabama won 41-23 over Texas A&M and play Tennessee at Bryant-Denny Stadium this Saturday, another 2:30 p.m. CDT kick, on CBS.
